properties.sfomuseum:description: Set of matchbooks issued by TWA (Trans World Airlines) promoting Lockheed L-1049 Super Constellation service; white matchbooks with color illustration of in-flight airplane and stewardess with text, “Welcome Aboard! TWA”; logotype on saddle:a. sleeve with illustration of people boarding TWA , with text, “Over 2,000,000 Passengers a Year Fly TWA Trans World Airlines”;b. matchbook with illustration of mission with text, “Los Angeles”;c. matchbook with illustration of Venice with text, “Italy”;d. matchbook with illustration of Chicago cityscape with text, “Chicago”;e. matchbook with illustration of New York City with text, “New York”;f. matchbook with illustration of Eiffel Tower with text, “Paris”;g. matchbook with illustration of Big Ben clock tower with text, “London”.
